text: SK Tirfing is a sports club in Harn√§s in Sweden. It was established on 20 January 1923. The club won the Swedish national men's bandy championship in the year of 1930. Between 1931 and 1942 the club played seven seasons in the Swedish top division. The club gave up bandy in 1981.
